recall: Jeff and william met at a bar and started a conversation. they realized they were both in the wine business and talked about  making a deal on some wine boxes to sell. at the airport the next day where they both were going to leave they struck a deal to sell $400 worth of wine for $600 and they were happy that they met and that everything worked out.

Alex and chloe dated for about 2 years and they went to a supermarket to do some thanksgiving shopping. alex had planned to propose in the supermarket and surprise chloe.he was very nervous but he eventually proposed and chloe said yes. she loved the design of the ring with the 2 pink diamonds and showed it off to a stranger. their friends who were hiding came out and took pictures of the proposal. alex paid $14 for the groceries in cash.

Ms.bianchi owns a wholesale cheese company in italy and she is looking to branch out in american supermarkets. she meets up with ms.morrison who is an owner of a supermarket and she tries to convince her to sell her cheese there. at first ms.morrison is not convinced and thinks that the import tax from italy would be too much money. but bianchi later convinces her to sell the cheese and ms.morrison hands her a check.

Thomas plans to break up with sadie and they meet at a restaurant. sadie is oblivious to this and is happy to see thomas. they are seated at a booth and sadie asks thomas whats wrong and he tells her that he wants to break up with her so that he can focus on his career. just then the waitress takes their orders and after she leaves sadie bursts out crying and kind of begs him not to break up with her. when they get the food, sadie takes half her sandwich, yells at thomas and tells him to never talk to her again and leaves. thomas tastes his burger which tastes fishy and hes disappointed.

Maria and henry have been dating for a while and they meet up to go to a lecture. maria wants to break up with henry and she does so in the lecture which is about the egyptian mummification process. they listen to the lecture and henry is upset about the fact that she wants to break up with him. she explains that she is getting on a plane and he later understands it and they both cry. the lecture ends.

Leon sees ariana in his college class and thinks that she looks familiar. he keeps glancing at her but she doesnt notice. he passes her a note asking if shes from california she says no and says maybe she has a twin. they pass notes back and forth throughot the class and leon eventually asks her out for a walk. she says yes and to meet her at 8 in front of her dorm. when class ends they meet and she explains that she has to go.

James and teresa are meeting for a date. james sees teresa hit her head on the glass door because shes looking at her phone and he thinks this is cute.when they meet he tells her he saw this and she asks him if hes ever been bit by a scorpion , he says no why. she says that everything has been different for her since she was. they order sushi rolls and japanese beer and sit closer together. james asks her to come to a concert with him at 8 and she says yes. he leaves because he has to leave by 3pm.

Sven and isabel are at the airport heading home from sapin after meeting her parents for the first time. sven is planning on proposing to isabel and is nervous. he puts the ring in his pocket. but when they get to the metal detector he forgets that its in his pocket and then decides to take it out and propose to isabel right there. she is so shy that she runs awaya nd sven finds her and she shouts yes and he says that she scared him for a second.
